title: After holidaying in London; BB10 runner-up Bani J is back in Mumbai
text:
Celebrity contestant Bani J might not have won the Bigg Boss trophy but she definitely has won the hearts of millions of viewers across the globe with her stint on Bigg Boss 10 .
Bani was one of the strongest contestants in the house and had a neck-to-neck competition with winner Manveer Gurjar , a commoner.
After coming out of the house, Bani flew to London with bestie Gauahar Khan to spend time with her family - sister, mother and niece.
READ ALSO: Bigg Boss runner up Bani J is making up for lost time in London with bestie Gauahar
After spending a few weeks in London with family, the badass actress is back to the bay - Mumbai.
She snap chatted it saying "She's back - Mumbai India"
READ ALSO: Bigg-Boss 10 runner-up Bani J visits Rannvijay Singha in London, meets the baby girl
Bani's huge fan following supported her throughout her journey in the Bigg Boss house and now they can't wait to see her on television again.
Let's see what's in store for us.
